	<tr>
		<td colspan="2"><hr class="sep" />I am a little curious what kind of hardware Nintendo used in the arcades back in the good old days. Their VS-systems I am quite familiar with but I guess they used other stuff aswell? I noticed they're starting to re-release arcade games on Switch, &quot;Mario Bros&quot; is coming up in just a few days but that ain't a VS-title as far as I know?<br />I started to google but all I get are links for MAME, more or less.<br />Is there a decent website with more techrelated stuff concerning these arcademachines?

		

		</td>
	</tr>
