		<td><b>Re: Technical information, Nintendo arcadegames?</b></td>
	</tr>
	<tr>
		<td colspan="2"><hr class="sep" />Unless an arcade board is used for numerous games, such as DECO Cassette System, Vs. System, Mega Play, Neo Geo MVS, or Capcom CPS, then each individual game on it is unlikely to warrant preparation of docs more detailed than needed to get the handful of extant games on that board working.

		

		</td>
	</tr>
	</table>


	<hr width="85%" />

	<table width="85%" cellspacing="3" cellpadding="0" border="0" align="center">
